title: COVID-19 EHS
description: Covid-19 EHS is  Coronavirus management App from EHS - Emirates Health Services, EHS. The App provides you with real-time Coronavirus stats in UAE in coordination with National Crisis & Emergency Management Authority UAE and EHS. The App provides facility to book and fully manage your Covid-19 Vaccine as well PCR appointments at your own convenience using your smart phone at any time. EHS is fully committed to provide digital COVID-19 channels to UAE community.
